Financial gain

Negligence (unintentional insiders)

Skills Level: Medium to High (depends on role)

Types of Insider Threats:

Malicious insiders â€“ intentionally steal or damage data

Negligent insiders â€“ click phishing links or misuse access

Typical Attacks:

